column2: SELECT p.objId, p.ra, p.dec, p.petror9#_r, p.dered_u as u, p.dered_g as g, p.dered_r as r, p.dered_i as i, s.z, z.spiral, z.elliptical, z.uncertain FROM galaxy AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN zooSpec AS z ON z.objid = p.objid WHERE p.ra between # and # and s.z between # and # and z.spiral = # or z.elliptical = #;
